    "body": "You at least need a source comment why exactly you are trying to do the fallback.\r\nAlso, the problem I have with the fallback is that we only need it for one specific dockerfile (for 20 others dockerfiles it works fine). If we one day break the efficient way of cloning the submodules (might happen), we likely won't find out because of the fallback."
